reviewText: This is great device.  We live in California and need to conserve water.  We have a big bucket of collected water, that we use to water our 100 houseplants.  The TERAPUMP is quick and easy to use to. transfer water into our watering can.  I'm so happy with it, this is the 3rd one I bought
